  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New puzzler from the creators of \"Klocki\", \"Zenge\", \"Hook\" and \"Art of Gravity\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Like our previous games, its intended to be a relaxing experience, thus there are no points, stars, tutorials, move counters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to push all the buttons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How do you do it? Well, thats the puzzle...</p>",
